column3: “This was amazing for my spine injury and nerve pain.  WoW!  My back has gel packs in the areas that hurt so much.... it's a nice, cold pain relief.  This made me couch locked only because I wanted to enjoy laying down without pain in my spine.  Berry OG has been the only one to help with my spine, but wow this is amazing too!  Tastes sweet, earthy, and woodsy.  Rolled this with a Green Apple Juicy Jay paper and damn ...”
“I love this strain. I was baked and painfree. This is the bomb”
“It's strong stuff, and it really helped my headache.”
“Had a fukd up day n dis made it all better. Relaxing, content, peaceful, mind clear, helps any physical pain, great couch 🌳 . ☮ 氣”

“Solid indica smoke that leads to a very pleasant body high. The dry mouth was a bit heavy, but overall there were very little drawbacks to this strain. I would recommend this potent strain to anyone looking for a relaxing indica experience.”

“Wow, amazing. This is probably the best indica ive copped. Granted, I live in nyc so im not used to the high quality kush of colorado or washington, but this was on a whole nother level. Highly recommend”
“really nice high...smokes well..smells great...really enjoyed this strain”
“This is awesome for any head aches or body aches. It’s also is nice if your going out and doing things!”

“This strain was really good, the taste is something im not a fan of, but still, it does relax you a lot, the mouth dry is kinda strong, so keep that in mind.
After the effect starts to run out you will feel really sleepy, i just had the best sleeping experience in the whole year, this thing is really good, something you must try out.”
“Great for assist with sleeping. Really Relaxed my body”
“Puts my pain and mind at peace.”
“A top three Indica. Body and mind at ease this is great for evenings. Mild flavor on inhale and a nice sour exhale. Big buds as well. I believe the oz was five buds.”
“Great Sleep Aid”
“Nice smooth taste...very relaxing.”
“Good help me relax”
“let you know in a few minutes in cincy”
“Great strain, great high wish it lasted a bit longer. Not quite the head high I'd like with my end of the day relaxation routine.”
“Love the taste and the buzz it gives omg 😗💨💨💨😆🤣😳😳😳”
“First hit I felt my back just get in place! Second hit I felt like I was so relaxed. 3rd hit let’s see.......”
“I’m more of a sativa person but this strain is ideal for putting on some good music or a funny show and just relaxing. It gives you a great body high and helps put you to sleep.”

“Made me feel very light-spirited.  Not sure if this actually gave me the munchies or if I was just really hungry from the day, but I ATE.  Very dense nugs, with a sweet yet sour aroma.  It definitely had that under the radar skunk smell, and the taste was sweet and earthy like I’d hoped for.  Great for a sweet and sound sleep - made my body feel yummy and lucid.”
“Lovely buds, tasty, good head high followed by a slow body relaxation.  Makes crap movies much better and my migraine go away.  Do it”
“Real good!!”
“love this strain very earthy taste I smoke shatter and wax and the double og in shatter is by far the best Indica I've had”
